	    	<li>Conference A, Set Guest Pin ____, Invite contacts through <a href="#">Phone</a> or <a href="#">Text</a></li>
	    	<li>Conference B, Set Guest Pin ____, <a href="#">Invite Contacts</a></li>
	    	<li>Conference C, Set Guest Pin ____, <a href="#">Invite Contacts</a></li>
	</ul> 
</div> <!--end hero-unit-->